-- Swiss asset manager GAM buys U.S.-based Singleterry Mansley
-- 
-- Thu Jun 05, 2014 11:56AM EDT
-- None



ZURICH, June 5 (Reuters) - Swiss asset management firm GAM Holding <GAMH.S> said on Thursday it was buying Singleterry Mansley Asset Management, a mortgage and asset-backed securities firm in the United States.

